name: Torpedo (Single Malt Glenfarelas)
additionalNotes:
Launched in 1996 with tobacco infused with 21 year old  Glenfarclas Single-Malt Scotch and long out of production, Texas Cigar Brothers stumbled upon a forgotten stock of these in their Honduran factory warehouse and offered those for sale in 2011.
